The function takes the following inputs
  cidr: A Cidr block in string format
  tag: A tag string that's added on created resources
  
The function creates the following resources
  A VPC on the given cidr block with dns hostnames and dns support enabled
  An internet gateway that is attached to the VPC
  Two subnets in availability zones a and b. You can modify the subnet properties in line 10.
  A route table that is associated with the subnets.
  A security group with a basic rule that allows all traffic within the security group.
